Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在『行动』的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有『结果』这个答案在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.27,0:00:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未有过例外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里 鲁路修的力量起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有着对任何对手都能下达绝对服从命令的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法从那个必然下逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.59,0:00:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界而行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是世界 人们却总是把和他的预想不同的结果摆在他眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.07,0:00:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并追求结果的『继续』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个『继续』与世界结合起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些人必须背负的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所应得到的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.41,0:00:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在何处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 13
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}莎莉和枪口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他既是虔诚的神的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是我们大家的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对妻子来说 他是优秀的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孩子来说 他是优秀的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我们祈祷他能够安息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再次把他埋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他再痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉要做爸爸的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像幼儿园的老师说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总有一天会找到喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比爸爸更加喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢也分很多种
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果莎莉真的喜欢那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那个人也真正的爱着莎莉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会从心底祝福你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.69,0:03:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 为什么要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在饭店劫持事件的时候看着电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得黑色骑士团有那么一点帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.85,0:03:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻的报道也有点偏向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于成田的事我也在留言版上写了“好厉害”一类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些完全没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也对成田的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我对你比较担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好哭过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在强忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过后会更加痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…哭够了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的做法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会坐收渔人之利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来改写事态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以审判者自居来得到胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话什么也改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由错误的过程得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉 等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一如既往的学生会室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很狡猾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很狡猾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的情况也只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你困扰了实在是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做法错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使得到了吻也不该高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为把友人的父亲卷了进来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对桐原说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说自己会走上修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是软弱的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说你只是把这当作游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在为止你已经杀了很多的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是由于你说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人也有家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有恋人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想说你还不了解这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的觉悟只是这种程度的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死克洛维斯的那时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.16,0:07:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么现在迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说因为感情而动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱在一起接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管说得多么的了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来也只不过是个只会夸口 脑筋迟钝的童贞小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经没有动摇和停止前进的权利了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了生存下去所需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是为了差别的对待而…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你杀了皇兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由错误的方法所得到的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴怎么说都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不是同母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是你的亲哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一方的自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种能随你意的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能变成安详的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有继续活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要踏上去吗 修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,资料载入和S4连接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信规程成立
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅直属部队来的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你参加下次的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被承认了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说又是做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与人正确的交往方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那个作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确京都那儿也有拜托我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的接受也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于日本解放战线来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起逃亡海外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还是会选择和我们联手才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报提供者 你叫迪哈鲁特是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到您是我的荣幸 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅投入了海军骑士队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要俘获解放战线的片濑少将
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:09:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局里已经开始准备特别报道节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂中校无法和片濑少将汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在日本解放战线不存在确定的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有作为逃亡资金的液态sakuradite可以依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其和科奈莉娅战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如优先帮助片濑少将逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做的事只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠毁灭科奈莉娅的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来解救日本解放战线的残存势力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成田遗忘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今要在这里夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胜算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始作战的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家按刚才的指示进行待机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有事的话过会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督现在还对于
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指定使用身为编号住民的你有点异议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我主张该使用的就要使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是以前的日本总理的儿子也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要制住这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获由海军部队来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是在海军捕获片濑的这段时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陆上进行援护射击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及捕获后对残党的歼灭作战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歼灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除目标以外不能让任何一人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向布里塔尼亚显示你的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是升迁的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是踩圣像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[踩圣像：日本江户时代，  幕府命令被怀疑为天主教徒的人踩踏基督和玛丽亚等\N圣像的一种制度,目的在于鉴别他们是否为天主教徒,这里意在试探朱雀的真意。]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在被他试探啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种可疑的人说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个少年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有与黑色骑士团有关系的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种怀疑你的事真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是联络到的更早点的话我就能想些办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该先把那个学生抓起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这需要确实的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过他与这女孩的对话一定可以找到接点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那家伙拥有操纵记忆的手段的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会像杰雷米亚一样失去地位与名誉然后死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 相反我还要得到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到和ZERO有关的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我一个人来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在迷茫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这是为了正义
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为这是正确的事才战斗到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所做的事真的能改变世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.07,0:13:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无论如何都要改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指会出现牺牲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现的不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是被卷进来死去的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此我们才不能止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论使用何种手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被人说是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能获取胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这样 只有成为修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让已流下的鲜血白流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才要付出更多的鲜血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不会强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回头的话就趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一同前进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 会和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才多亏你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C. 我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经不能再经历相同的失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指挥中心呼叫全队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下潜 下潜 下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}特别镇压部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}检查使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的部队在陆上进行援护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意别击沉了目标的油轮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部队自由使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 各部队自由使用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不出击吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅的行动比想像的更快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在行动的话我们会和他们一起被打败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护射击开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限定使用武器为小型的一点射击子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心别引爆了液态sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚军什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人 从水中过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,202号 503号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开9时方向过来的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种已经不是战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是职业军人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪儿泄露了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不知道所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四圣剑也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫他们搬救兵过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们没有单方面联络他们的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道让我告诉士兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们死得毫无意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…投降…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对贵军投降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通用频道有投降宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是拖延时间的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下了 继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁真的在黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死 这样的话会来不及的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO什么时候才会行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是祈祷ZERO不仅仅是个理想主义者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KnightMare已经上了油轮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脱的路径应该只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么小心的保存着液态sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 不快一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.53,0:17:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然引爆液态sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把布里塔尼亚军卷进来的自决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有收到这种情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在突入科奈莉娅所在的本阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管其他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把结果作为最优先考虑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想让日本解放战线的血白流的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到我军的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示我们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话不是和成田的时候一样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以日本解放战线为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻被吸引注意力的敌方本阵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这种主意的话虽然不错 但还略显不足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃跑吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都决定要干了就干脆把敌人的战力削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把无能的日本解放战线作为活的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然ZERO是优秀的素材
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混乱的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多 让我再看的更多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你牵引的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,204信号消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里克逊和308合流进行支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全队报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 全队报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的自爆了吗 片濑少将
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是本队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道以油轮为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急启动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情报是从哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在驾驶员上机以前把KnightMare打到海里去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲二式跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下 这里就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能忍受一而再 再而三的愚弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在启动之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为能在KnightMare战里胜过我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把驾驶舱打破把你拖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 你的做法什么也改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只一味追求结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白别人的痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成田的债要在这儿还了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个白壳的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么随便的用生命作为诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一个杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是你这个家伙来阻碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要让人们无意义的流血
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.80,0:20:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 这也是一种结果了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot 注意后面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何东西都会产生破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.41,0:23:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候都会产生迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.80,0:23:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心底一点一点堆积的被称为感情的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:23:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会成为明天的支柱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.60,0:24:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会成为昨日的沉淀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所应得到的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我自身之中
